          From native iOS and Android apps to cross-platform solutions, we create mobile experiences that users love.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Native iOS Development -->
        <div class="service-card text-center group scroll-animate" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
